    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Katon)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> E, F, Mas</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You shape your Chakra into a crimson, predatory bird that dives at the target. Make a ranged attack using your held weapon, which deals an additional 3d6 fire damage (not multiplied on critical hits). When performing this technique, you take 3d6 damage.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra and 1 HP to increase the damage by 1d6, up to 1d6 per level or 10d6 total.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The third step allows you to ignore the base damage you suffer (but not the empower damage). The fifth step allows you to ignore the damage you would take when empowering this technique.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
